snippet.title: Ryouma de Yuku on snes9-sx2?
snippet.description:
http://bsxproj.superfamicom.org/

On the updated snes9x-sx2, I tried loading up Ryouma de Yuku Zenpen.
However, I don't know what caused my stats to get so jacked...? Or why the boat in that one cutscene is going the opposite direction... huh...

I'll ask someone else about it later, I guess.
